578
00:35:28,420 --> 00:35:30,660
♪Tanpa sengaja membalikkan kepala♪

579
00:35:31,100 --> 00:35:35,020
♪Galaksi mana yang sedang aku arungi?♪

580
00:35:35,180 --> 00:35:41,900
♪Menatap bintang mana
